    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The FEA model ensemble demonstrates sufficient credibility for the intended use. All three QoIs are within the pre-specified 10% acceptance bound. E/uval ratios for stiffness and yield force are within the 1.96 threshold. The single below-required factor (Test conditions) is accepted as a documented limitation given that the ASTM F1717 standard prescribes a single test configuration and the regulatory context does not require multi-condition validation for this device class. Uncertainty in the force-at-40mm result is addressed qualitatively in the assessment narrative; the overall evidence package supports an Accepted decision at Medium assurance level.",
